'''Dagobah mud cake''' was a type of food enjoyed by a [[Unidentified green bounty hunter|green bounty hunter]] who was present at [[Ban Papeega]]'s interrogation of [[Thurlow Harris]] on [[Centares/Legends|Centares]]. It was served with [[junk beetle]]s. The dish shared its name with the swamp [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dagobah/Legends|Dagobah]].

